  "title": "运营助理（Operations Assistant）",
  "description": "<h2>连锁餐饮代运营公司招聘</h2><h3>Chain F&B Operations Management Company – Hiring</h3><h3>招聘职位 / Position</h3><p><strong>运营助理（Operations Assistant）</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>工作地点 / Location：</strong> 新加坡 CBD</p><h2>岗位职责 / Job Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>负责起草、整理及管理合作合约、招租合约及相关行政文件；<br />Draft, prepare and manage cooperation agreements, tenancy agreements and related administrative documents;</p></li><li><p>协助处理餐饮相关执照申请，包括餐饮执照（SFA）及酒牌（Liquor Licence），并跟进审批流程；<br />Assist in applying for F&B-related licences, including SFA food shop licences and liquor licences, and follow up on approval status;</p></li><li><p>统筹公司用工配额，协助办理及跟进工人准证申请（WP / SP 等）；<br />Coordinate manpower quota matters and assist with work pass applications (WP / SP, etc.);</p></li><li><p>负责食阁及连锁餐饮项目的人事招聘与员工档案管理；<br />Handle recruitment and staff records management for food court and chain F&B outlets;</p></li><li><p>薪资计算，并整理、统计及汇报财务与销售数据；<br />Prepare payroll calculations and compile financial and sales data reports;</p></li><li><p>协作对接客户，配合项目运营进度，处理日常沟通与行政支持；<br />Liaise with clients and support daily communications and operational coordination;</p></li><li><p>协助上级完成其他运营及行政后勤相关工作。<br />Perform other administrative and operational duties as assigned.</p></li></ul><h2>岗位要求 / Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>新加坡公民 / PR / LTVP 持有人；<br />Singapore Citizen / PR / LTVP holder;</p></li><li><p>具备新加坡本地工作经验，熟悉本地商业政策、人事及行政流程；<br />Local working experience in Singapore with knowledge of business, HR and administrative processes;</p></li><li><p>英语听说读写良好，能独立处理合约及正式文件；<br />Proficient in spoken and written English, able to handle contracts and official documents independently;</p></li><li><p>工作细心、有责任感，具备良好的沟通与协调能力；<br />Detail-oriented, responsible, with good communication and coordination skills;</p></li><li><p>有餐饮行业、食阁、连锁品牌或代运营公司经验者优先。<br />Experience in F&B, food courts, chain brands or operations management companies is an advantage.</p></li></ul><h2>工作待遇 / Employment Benefits</h2><ul><li><p><strong>薪资 / Salary：</strong> SGD 3,000 – 4,000（视经验而定 / based on experience）</p></li><li><p><strong>工作时间 / Working Hours：</strong> 周一至周五 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM</p></li><li><p><strong>工作制度 / Work Arrangement：</strong> 五天工作制 / 5-day work week</p></li><li><p><strong>年假 / Annual Leave：</strong> 14 天</p></li><li><p>享有新加坡法定假期及公司其他福利<br />Entitled to Singapore public holidays and other company benefits</p></li></ul>",
